data.description: This beautiful home is in need of a new owner! USDA Eligible and 100% financing!! Once you come inside you will fall in love with the open concept kitchen and living space. The kitchen boasts granite countertops, custom cabinets and gorgeous lighting. You can snuggle on the couch and enjoy a cup of hot cocoa by the fireplace with a good movie. The bedrooms are spacious and the master suite will envelope you in relaxation after a busy day at work. Make your appointment today to see this house!
